// Aide :
Drag and drop : https://www.javascripttutorial.net/web-apis/javascript-drag-and-drop/
Pure CSS X : https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10019797/pure-css-close-button
Drag and drop : https://www.kirupa.com/html5/drag.htm
Placer after un élément: https://attacomsian.com/blog/javascript-insert-element-after  // appendChild : mettre dans un élément
Taille d'élément : https://code-boxx.com/get-width-height-elements-javascript/
Position du curseur dans un élément : https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3234256/find-mouse-position-relative-to-element/42111623#42111623
Scrollbar : https://medium.com/frontend-development-with-js/how-to-hide-scrollbar-and-visible-only-scrolling-79cc3472e503
Event triggered only on parent : https://stackoverflow.com/a/53815609
Background-color take defined size : https://stackoverflow.com/questions/8541081/css-set-a-background-color-which-is-50-of-the-width-of-the-window
Disable all links : https://stackoverflow.com/questions/8002579/how-to-disable-all-a-links-using-javascript-in-firefox-and-chrome

Github Page : https://pages.github.com/

